"Dockside follows where the Dock goes, sometimes the macOS display settings may interfere with this. To properly move Dock (and the Dockside) to the other display/screen/monitor.\n\nNavigate to 'System Settings' > 'Displays' > Click on 'Arrange...' and move the white menu bar to the screen you want to set as primary. \n\nThis will make that display your main display in macOS with Dock in it. Dockside will automatically move here too and work as expected." = "Dockside 會跟隨 Dock 的位置，但 macOS 的顯示設置有時會影響這一行為。要將 Dock（以及 Dockside）正確移動到另一塊顯示器/屏幕/顯示器，请按以下步驟操作。\n\n前往“係統設置” > “顯示器”，點擊“排列...”，并把白色菜單栏拖到你想設為主屏的顯示器。\n\n這樣该顯示器就會成為 macOS 的主顯示器，Dock 也會在其上顯示。Dockside 會自動移動到這裡并正常工作。";
