"You have enabled the advanced preference setting of the Finder to disable the Desktop features. All icons on the Desktop will disappear the next time the Finder will be launched. They will be restored when you uncheck this option.\nNo files will be moved or deleted. As before, you can access all files currently lying on the Desktop via the folder “Desktop” in your private home folder. You can access all disk volumes via the “Computer” window of the Finder." = "您已啟用 Finder 的高級偏好設置以禁用桌麵功能。下次 Finder 啟動時，桌麵上的所有圖標都會消失；當您取消该選項時會恢復。\n不會移動或删除任何文件。和以前一樣，您仍可通過個人主目錄中的“桌麵”文件夾访問桌麵上的文件，并可通過 Finder 的“電腦”窗口访問所有磁盤捲。";
"You now have full access to every feature with no subscriptions, no recurring charges, and no hidden fees. This app is lovingly crafted by an indie developer, and your support means the world to me. Enjoy the app, all future updates, and know that you’ve supported independent development!" = "您現在可以完整使用所有功能，沒有訂閱、沒有重復收費、也沒有隱藏費用。這款應用由独立開發者精心打造，您的支持意義重大。祝您使用愉快并享受未來的更新，也感謝您支持独立開發！";
"You now have full access to every features and make sure to join our Discord server for active support. This app is lovingly crafted by an indie developer, and your support means the world to me. Enjoy the app, all future updates, and know that you’ve supported independent development! 🙏🏽" = "您現在已獲得所有功能的完整權限，并请加入我们的 Discord 服務器以獲得活躍支持。這款應用由独立開發者精心打造，您的支持意義重大。祝您使用愉快并享受未來的更新，也感謝您支持独立開發！🙏🏽";
"Your license has been successfully deactivated on this machine.\nThank you for your continued support! Your purchase not only allows me to keep this app up and running but also helps me, as an indie developer, to enhance the app with new features and improvements.\n\nShould you need to activate the license on another device, you're all set to do so. If you encounter any issues or have suggestions, don't hesitate to get in touch. Your feedback is invaluable!\n\nThank you once again for being part of this journey!" = "您的许可證已在此設备上成功停用。\n感謝您一直以來的支持！您的購買不僅讓這款應用持續更新，也幫助我這個独立開發者添加新功能與改進。\n\n如需在其他設备上激活许可證，現在即可進行。如果遇到問題或有建議，歡迎隨時聯係。您的反馈非常宝贵！\n\n再次感謝您成為這段旅程的一部分！";
"Your trial period has ended. To continue using the app and unlock all features, please purchase a one-time license.\nThis app is lovingly crafted by an indie developer, and your support ensures future updates and features. Thank you!" = "您的試用期已結束。要繼續使用并解鎖所有功能，请購買一次性许可證。\n這款應用由独立開發者倾心打造，您的支持將帶來更多更新與功能。謝謝！";
