"Disables macOS Desktop features such as drag and drop, right-click menu, and desktop icons to prevent interference with Dockside behaviors. Nothing is deleted, and all features will be restored to their original state when you disable this option." = "禁用 macOS 桌麵功能（如拖放、右鍵菜單和桌麵圖標）以避免與 Dockside 行為冲突。不會删除任何内容，關闭该選項後會恢復原狀。";
"Disables the delay when showing the hidden Dock (i.e., sets 'autohide-delay' Dock property).\n\nThe action is reversible so not to worry,  the Dock auto-hide delay property will be restored to system defaults when you uncheck this option." = "禁用顯示隱藏 Dock 時的延迟（設置 Dock 属性“autohide-delay”）。\n\n该操作可恢復，因此不用担心；取消勾選後將恢復係統默認的自動隱藏延迟。";
