"Dock Auto-Hide Time Modifier:" = "Dock 自動隱藏時间修正:";
"Dockside Auto-Hide Delay:" = "Dockside 自動隱藏延迟:";
"Dockside creates a working directory here. Dockside stores temporary files, notes & items dropped from external sources like web here. Also stores the copies of the local items here when 'Store Only Item References' is disabled. " = "Dockside 在此创建工作目錄。Dockside 會在此存放臨時文件、筆記以及來自網頁等外部來源拖入的項目。當“僅存储引用”被關闭時，本地項目的副本也會存放在此。";
"Dockside follows where the Dock goes, by default (automatic mode).Sometimes the macOS display settings may interfere with this. To properly move the Dock (and the Dockside) to the other screen Navigate to 'System Settings' > 'Displays' > Click on 'Arrange...' and move the white menu bar to the screen you want to set as primary. This will make that display your main display in macOS with Dock in it.\nDockside will automatically move here too and work as expected. To force move the Dockside to one of your screens, select from the below." = "默認情况下 Dockside 會跟隨 Dock 的位置（自動模式）。有時 macOS 顯示設置會影響這一行為。要將 Dock（以及 Dockside）正確移動到另一塊屏幕，请前往“係統設置”>“顯示器”>“排列...”，并把白色菜單栏拖到你想設為主屏的顯示器。這樣该顯示器將成為 macOS 主顯示器并顯示 Dock。\nDockside 也會自動移動到此并正常工作。要強制將 Dockside 移到某個屏幕，请在下方選擇。";
"Dockside occasionally shows a few useful tips near the menu bar icon that are relevant from time to time. However, if the menu bar icon is disabled or if you have installed menu bar customization apps (like Bartender or Ice), Dockside will automatically disable the popups to reduce annoyance." = "Dockside 偶爾會在菜單栏圖標附近顯示一些有用提示。如果菜單栏圖標被禁用，或你安裝瞭菜單栏管理應用（如 Bartender 或 Ice），Dockside 會自動關闭這些弹窗以減少打擾。";
"Dockside will additionally monitor the specified files location for new items and automatically add them to the Files shelf for easy access. You can continue to drag and drop to the Files shelf even when this is enabled. The dragged items that are downloaded will still be saved in the work directory of Dockside and not in this monitored directory." = "Dockside 會额外監控指定的文件位置以檢测新項目，并自動添加到文件貨架。即使啟用此功能，你仍可繼續拖放到文件貨架。通過拖放下載的項目仍會保存在 Dockside 的工作目錄中，而不是该監控目錄。";
"Dockside will automatically fade out to keep your Dock area distraction free, it will bounce back to llife when dragging is detected or mouse activity is detected on the Dockside. This option is only applicable when Dock and the Dockside is NOT in auto-hide mode. " = "Dockside 會自動淡齣以保持 Dock 區域清爽，當檢测到拖拽或鼠標活動時會恢復顯示。此選項僅在 Dock 和 Dockside 未處於自動隱藏模式時適用。";
"Dockside will be a bit more dynamic with it's size changes in response to the Dock size changes. The feature impacts the CPU resource utilisation slightly due to the need for polling Dock size changes." = "Dockside 會更動態地響應 Dock 尺寸变化。由於需要輪询 Dock 大小，此功能會略微增加 CPU 資源占用。";
