"Enables advanced logging for debugging purposes. Enable this only when requested by the developer, as it may impact app performance. This will generate detailed app logs locally for debugging purposes. The logs collected during this process contain no personal, behavioural or machine-specific data and are intended solely to help the developer debug issues with the app. The logs can be shared via email to the developer using the download button. " = "啟用高級日志以便調試。僅在開發者要求時開啟，因為可能影響應用性能。此功能會在本地生成详細日志。收集的日志不包含個人、行為或機器特定數據，僅用於幫助開發者調試問題。可通過下載按钮將日志發送給開發者。";
"Enter a comma-separated list of simple filename patterns. Use * as a wildcard to match any characters. For example, *.log, temp*, backup* will match any files with a .log extension, files starting with temp, or files starting with backup." = "输入以逗号分隔的簡單文件名模式。使用 * 作為通配符匹配任意字符。例如：*.log、temp*、backup* 將匹配 .log 擴展名的文件、以 temp 開頭或以 backup 開頭的文件。";
"Feature Request" = "功能请求";
"Files downloaded from web, copies of originals dragged to shelf and other temporary files are auto-deleted if they are more than 30 days old" = "从網頁下載的文件、拖入貨架的原始文件副本以及其他臨時文件在超過 30 天後會被自動删除";
"Full Screen Apps" = "全屏應用";
