"If an email ID was not provided at the time of purchase, just add any email address here to proceed with the license activation." = "如果購買時未提供郵箱，请在此填寫任意郵箱以繼續激活许可證。";
"Ignore dragging (shelf will not activate)" = "忽略拖拽（貨架不激活）";
"Ignored Apps" = "已忽略的應用";
"In addition to monitoring the Screenshots location, Dockside will monitor the Clipboard only for screenshots and automatically save them to the above location for later use. This currently only works with native macOS screenshots app as this is triggered based on the keyboard shortcuts." = "除監控截圖位置外，Dockside 還會僅針對截圖監控剪贴板，并自動保存到上述位置以便後續使用。目前僅適用於 macOS 原生截圖應用，因為它依赖鍵盤快捷鍵触發。";
"Keyboard Shortcuts - General" = "鍵盤快捷鍵 - 通用";
"Launch & Updates" = "啟動與更新";
"License Key" = "许可證密钥";
"License Status" = "许可證狀態";
"Monitor Directory:" = "監控目錄:";
"Monitor Directory" = "監控目錄";
"Move the file" = "移動文件";
"Moves the original file to the target location instead of copying." = "將原始文件移動到目標位置而不是復制。";
"Offsets the auto-hide delay for Dockside (not the Dock). Currently set to 0.\n\nDockside will automatically inherit the Dock settings, if the system defaults has been overriden Dockside will detect this too (i.e., 'autohide-delay' and 'autohide-time-modifier' Dock properties). \n\nIdeally, you don't have to modify this, Dockside should work this out for you but if you need to further tune the timings based on your likings, feel free to change this (the dot indicates default setting of 0). If you encounter any issues, reach out to the developer via email/Discord." = "用於偏移 Dockside（非 Dock）的自動隱藏延迟，當前為 0。\n\nDockside 會自動繼承 Dock 設置；若係統默認被修改，Dockside 也會檢测到（例如 ‘autohide-delay’ 與 ‘autohide-time-modifier’）。\n\n通常無需修改，Dockside 會自動處理；如需進一步微調時间，可自行調整（圆點表示默認值 0）。如遇問題，请通過郵件/Discord 聯係開發者。";
"Only screenshot images are shown in the shelf when this is enabled. Dockside looks for screenshot image attribute (xattr) to detect screenshots, not all images are shown if this is ticked." = "啟用後，貨架只顯示截圖圖片。Dockside 會通過截圖圖像属性（xattr）識别截圖，因此不會顯示所有圖片。";
"Open Sentry" = "打開 Sentry";
"Positioning" = "位置";
"Prevents shelves from revealing while hovering." = "防止悬停時貨架展開。";
"Remove file from shelf" = "从貨架移除文件";
"Remove the app from the ignore list, edit like a text editor and click on Apply to see the changes. You may need to restart the Dockside app for the changes to take effect." = "从忽略列表中移除應用，像编辑文本一樣修改後點擊“應用”以生效。可能需要重啟 Dockside 才能生效。";
"Removed from the shelf, original is kept intact." = "已从貨架移除，原始文件保持不变。";
"Reset \"Dont Ask Me\" Warnings" = "重置“不要再問我”警告";
"Resets macOS Accessibility and System Events (Automation) permissions for Dockside app. Dockside will then request for the relevant permissions again when required on launch." = "重置 Dockside 的 macOS 輔助功能與係統事件（自動化）權限。Dockside 會在需要時再次请求相關權限。";
"Select All" = "全選";
"Select Screen" = "選擇屏幕";
"Set the number of recent downloads to display in the Screenshots & Downloads shelf, up to a maximum of 50. When it exceeds, the oldest is automatically removed by Dockside to make way for the new Download." = "設置截圖與下載貨架中顯示的最近下載數量（最多 10 個）。超過時 Dockside 會自動移除最舊的項目以騰齣空间。";
"Set the number of recent files to display in the Files shelf, up to a maximum of 50. When it exceeds, the oldest is automatically removed by Dockside to make way for the new item." = "設置文件貨架中顯示的最近文件數量（最多 15 個）。超過時 Dockside 會自動移除最舊的項目以騰齣空间。";
"Set the number of recent notes to display in the Files shelf, up to a maximum of 50. When it exceeds, the oldest is automatically removed by Dockside to make way for the new item." = "設置文件貨架中顯示的最近筆記數量（最多 10 個）。超過時 Dockside 會自動移除最舊的項目以騰齣空间。";
"Set the number of recent screenshots to display in the Screenshots & Downloads shelf, up to a maximum of 50. When it exceeds, the oldest is automatically removed by Dockside to make way for the new Screenshot." = "設置截圖與下載貨架中顯示的最近截圖數量（最多 10 個）。超過時 Dockside 會自動移除最舊的項目以騰齣空间。";
"Set the sensitivity for revealing Dockside when hovering near it in auto-hide mode. Higher sensitivity makes Dockside appear more quickly, while lower sensitivity reduces accidental reveals. You can also use the 'Option' hotkey to stop Dockside from revealing temporarily. " = "設置在自動隱藏模式下，鼠標靠近時顯示 Dockside 的靈敏度。靈敏度越高顯示越快，越低可減少誤触。你也可以按住 Option 熱鍵臨時阻止 Dockside 顯示。";
"Shelf Visibility" = "貨架可見性";
"Show Downloads Area" = "顯示下載區域";
"Show Screenshots & Downloads Shelf" = "顯示屏幕截圖與下載貨架";
"Show Screenshots Area" = "顯示截圖區域";
"Store a copy of original file in shelf" = "在貨架中保存原始文件副本";
"Stores a copy in the shelf instead of a reference." = "在貨架中保存副本而不是引用。";
"Support Email" = "支持郵箱";
"Temporarily disables drop area activation." = "臨時禁用拖放區域激活。";
"Temporarily reveals shelves in auto-hide mode." = "在自動隱藏模式下臨時顯示貨架。";
"The Dockside shelf is activated based on the triggers selected here, to disable the activation completely use the disable activation toggle." = "Dockside 貨架會根據這裡選擇的触發方式激活；若要完全禁用激活，请使用“禁用激活”開關。";
"The following settings control the macOS Dock appearance and behavior which you can adjust directly in System Preferences > Desktop & Dock. These are only meant to be useful shortcuts." = "以下設置控制 macOS Dock 的外觀與行為，你也可以在“係統設置”>“桌麵與 Dock”中直接調整。這些只是便捷的快捷方式。";
"The items downloaded from web, copies of the original items (when items are stored as copies rather than reference) will be physically deleted when you remove the item from shelf. This is particularly useful when working with temp or one-time files." = "从網頁下載的項目、原始項目的副本（以副本而非引用方式存储時）在从貨架移除時會被物理删除。這對處理臨時或一次性文件特别有用。";
"The shelf expands automatically when you hover directly over an empty space or the expand button - provided there are more files to display.\n\nHowever, if you're hovering over a file already visible on the shelf, it won't expand immediately allowing you to browse them. Once you're done browsing, simply move your mouse near the expand button to express the intent of seeing more in the shelf, and the shelf will expand automatically." = "當你把鼠標悬停在空白區域或展開按钮上時，如果有更多文件可顯示，貨架會自動展開。\n\n如果你悬停在已顯示的文件上，為瞭便於浏覽，貨架不會立刻展開。浏覽完毕後，將鼠標移到展開按钮附近以表示想查看更多内容，貨架會自動展開。";
"This is the location where your Screenshots destination is set to in your macOS. Only the images that are recognised as a screenshot is shown here (based on the image attribute)." = "這是 macOS 中設置的截圖保存位置。這裡只會顯示被識别為截圖的圖片（基於圖像属性）。";
"This will hide the Dockside, and its behavior is similar to that of the Dock. It will appear when the mouse is near either the Dock or the Dockside. Dockside will automatically enter hide mode when an app is in full-screen mode or if the Dock is hidden. You don't need to enable this manually for it to happen." = "此選項會隱藏 Dockside，其行為類似 Dock。當鼠標靠近 Dock 或 Dockside 時會顯示。若有應用處於全屏或 Dock 被隱藏，Dockside 會自動進入隱藏模式，無需手動啟用。";
"Usage Tips & Tricks" = "使用技巧";
"Version: %@" = "版本：%@";
"Website" = "網站";
"When Clop is available, Dockside will automatically optimise image or video or PDF dragged to the shelf. You can always manually do this via right-click menu but this option will automatically do it for you every time you drop a file to the shelf." = "當 Clop 可用時，Dockside 會自動優化拖入貨架的圖片、視頻或 PDF。你也可以通過右鍵菜單手動執行，但此選項會在每次拖放時自動完成。";
"When Dockside is hidden away in auto-hide mode or when apps are in full screen mode, taking the mouse near the Dock will also reveal the Dockside. When this option is disabled, Dockside will reveal when the mouse is near the Dockside." = "當 Dockside 處於自動隱藏模式或應用處於全屏時，將鼠標移到 Dock 附近也會顯示 Dockside。禁用此選項後，只有靠近 Dockside 才會顯示。";
"When a file or folder is dragged to a destination, it is automatically removed from Dockside. But, if you need to temporarily remove the item on draging out then hold the Option or Shift key when dragging out." = "當文件或文件夾被拖到目標位置時，會自動从 Dockside 移除。如果你希望拖齣時僅臨時移除，请在拖動時按住 Option 或 Shift 鍵。";
"When enabled, Dockside will automatically downoad a .webp image file as a .png image file. The file sizes will vary compared to the source image file. Uses native libraries." = "啟用後，Dockside 會自動將 .webp 圖片下載為 .png 文件。文件大小可能與原始文件不同。使用原生庫處理。";
"When enabled, Dockside will display the items matching the pattern in the shelf, but these items will be excluded when performing bulk deletions from shelf." = "啟用後，Dockside 會顯示匹配模式的項目，但在執行批量删除時會排除這些項目。";
"When enabled, Dockside will ignore plain text drag and the shelf is not activated during the drag. You can still drop it to the shelf though. Note that plain text drags are default delayed by 0.4ms to reduce false triggers" = "啟用後，Dockside 會忽略纯文本拖拽，拖拽期间貨架不會被激活。你仍可將其拖放到貨架。注意：纯文本拖拽默認延迟 0.4ms 以減少誤触。";
"When enabled, both shelves are shown when the mouse is hovered over either of the shelf. To show them independently, disable this option." = "啟用後，當鼠標悬停在任一貨架上時會同時顯示兩個貨架。若要分别顯示，请禁用此選項。";
"When enabled, the app crash report (when app crashes) is automatically sent to the developer via Sentry. The log may contain device info such as OS version, machine type and app crash report for debugging purposes only. Disable it when you don't need to report app crashes." = "啟用後，當應用崩溃時會通過 Sentry 自動嚮開發者發送崩溃報告。日志可能包含係統版本、設备型号及崩溃信息，僅用於調試。若不需要報告崩溃，请關闭此項。";
