"A lightweight file shelf that keeps your files and folders at your fingertips beside the Dock." = "一個輕量的文件貨架，讓你的文件和文件夾在 Dock 旁触手可及。";
"Hey, I'm Prajwal, the developer behind Dockside. I love making lightweight and useful apps like Dockside, a streamlined file shelf designed to keep your files and folders at your fingertips beside the Dock.

Dockside doesn't collect or share any of your data. It only uses the internet for a license check, and after that everything stays on your device. Your privacy is as important to me as it is to you. If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out — I'd love to hear from you. Thanks for supporting indie development!" = "你好，我是 Prajwal，这款应用的开发者！😊 我喜欢制作轻量且实用的应用，比如 Dockside —— 一个简洁的文件货架，让你的文件和文件夹在 Dock 旁触手可及。

Dockside 不会收集或分享你的任何数据。它只在进行许可证验证时使用网络，之后一切都保留在你的设备上。🔒 你的隐私对我和对你一样重要。如果你有任何问题或反馈，欢迎联系我——我很乐意听到你的声音。感谢支持独立开发！🙏";

